legacy.full_text: This morning I had the honour and pleasure to call on His Majesty King Letsie III of the Kingdom of Lesotho. We had a warm and friendly discussion on 🇨🇳China-🇱🇸Lesotho friendship and cooperative relations. https://t.co/4jDOBrLbaY

We donated "love parcels" to 150 children from 6 orphanages in 🇱🇸Lesotho. https://t.co/OCnvOII7ug

Congrats to 🇨🇳SINOHYDRO on the strong partnership with 🇱🇸Lesotho and 🇿🇦South African conterparts! Wish a complete success to Phase II of the Lesotho Highlands Water Project which will bring long term benefits to both Lesotho and South Africa! https://t.co/ey98ph2hEB

I am glad that 🇨🇳SINOHYDRO is one of the main contractors of this megaproject. https://t.co/UdwWAX4Q4z
